<page>
    <shortlink>api nf lower function</shortlink>
   <topic>NF_LOWER Function</topic>
    <description>Returns a string that is lowercased except for the first letter.</description>
    
   <prototype>Output_String as C = NF_LOWER(C String)</prototype>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>String</name>
         <description>A character string.</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
  
   <discussion>
NF_LOWER() leaves the case of the first character of String unchanged, and converts the rest of String to lower case.
   </discussion>
   <example><![CDATA[
nf_lower("ALPHA SOFTWARE CORP") -> "Alpha software corp"
]]></example>
   <see>
     <ref link="api character case functions">Character Case Functions</ref>
   </see>
<terms>string,case,function,rest</terms>
</page>